% a=(a "b ")
% x=(x y)
% args ${a}${x}
a
b x
y
% args ${(o}a}${x}
a
b x
y

OK so far, but ...
setopt shwordsplit

% args ${a}${x}
a
b
x
y
% args ${(o}a}${x}
a
bx
y

Given, that (o) in this case does nothing I expect the second subst to
result in 4 words as well.

